@startuml
title Éclairage (Phares)
participant "UI (React)" as UI
participant "Backend" as Server
participant "ESP32" as ESP

== État Permanent ==
UI -> Server: { "action": "HEADLIGHTS", "state": "ON" }
Server -> ESP: { "cmd": "LIGHT", "power": 1 }

== Appel de Phares ==
UI -> Server: { "action": "FLASH_LIGHTS" }
Server -> ESP: { "cmd": "BLINK", "pattern": "SHORT_3" }
note right of ESP: L'ESP gère le timing du clignotement\nen local pour éviter la latence réseau.
@enduml